, or the presiding officer may order that a brief"}]}, {"t": ".09 Decisions and Orders.", "p": "/us/md/exec/comar/12.04.03.09", "et": "section", "sc": "12.04.03.09", "rp": "12|04|03|.09", "sp": "library|Code of Maryland Regulations|12|04|03|.09", "c": [{"t": "A.", "p": "/us/md/exec/comar/12.04.03.09#A", "et": "para", "sc": "12.04.03.09A", "rp": "12|04|03|.09|A.", "x": "A decision by the Commission shall be made by a majority of the members pre"}, {"t": "B.", "p": "/us/md/exec/comar/12.04.03.09#B", "et": "para", "sc": "12.04.03.09B", "rp": "12|04|03|.09|B.", "x": "The presiding officer shall prepare the Commission's final decision and ord"}, {"t": "C.", "p": "/us/md/exec/comar/12.04.03.09#C", "et": "para", "sc": "12.04.03.09C", "rp": "12|04|03|.09|C.", "x": "The Commission shall deliver or mail a copy of the decision and order and a"}, {"t": "D.", "p": "/us/md/exec/comar/12.04.03.09#D", "et": "para", "sc": "12.04.03.09D", "rp": "12|04|03|.09|D.", "x": "Unless specified otherwise, orders of the presiding officer or the Commissi"}]}, {"t": ".10 Request for Reconsideration.", "p": "/us/md/exec/comar/12.04.03.10", "et": "section", "sc": "12.04.03.10", "rp": "12|04|03|.10", "sp": "library|Code of Maryland Regulations|12|04|03|.10", "c": [{"t": "A.", "p": "/us/md/exec/comar/12.04.03.10#A", "et": "para", "sc": "12.04.03.10A", "rp": "12|04|03|.10|A.", "x": "A party may request reconsideration of a final decision by the Commission."}, {"t": "B.", "p": "/us/md/exec/comar/12.04.03.10#B", "et": "para", "sc": "12.04.03.10B", "rp": "12|04|03|.10|B.", "c": [{"t": "(1)", "p": "/us/md/exec/comar/12.04.03.10#B(1)", "et": "para", "sc": "12.04.03.10B(1)", "rp": "12|04|03|.10|B.|(1)", "x": "Be in writing;"}, {"t": "(2)", "p": "/us/md/exec/comar/12.04.03.10#B(2)", "et": "para", "sc": "12.04.03.10B(2)", "rp": "12|04|03|.10|B.|(2)", "x": "Be received by the presiding officer issuing the decision not later than 10"}, {"t": "(3)", "p": "/us/md/exec/comar/12.04.03.10#B(3)", "et": "para", "sc":